==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Firelock
<hw>Fire"lock`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An old form of gunlock, as the
flintlock, which ignites the priming by a spark; perhaps originally, a
matchlock. Hence, a gun having such a lock.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fireman</ent>⟦br⟧
